<h2 align="center"><font face="Times New Roman">Contacting Us</font></h2>

<p align="center"><b><font face="Arial"><a href="phonefax.htm" title="Phone and Fax numbers"> Phone/Fax
Numbers for all DEP programs</a>&nbsp; |&nbsp; <a href="emer24.htm">24-hour emergency and
information phone lines</a></font></b></p>

<p align="center"><b><font face="Arial"><a href="directio.htm">Directions to DEP
Offices</a>&nbsp; | <a href="http://www.phone.state.ct.us/phonesearch.asp">State
Employees Phone Directory</a> <img border="0" src="../../images/arrow7.gif" alt="Leaving DEP Website Arrow" width="70" height="12"></font></b></p>

<p><font face="Times New Roman">Feel free to <b><a href="phonefax.htm">call</a> </b>
us during normal
business hours - Monday through Friday, 8:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. - to speak to staff or,
leave a message any other time of the day. <strong>Fax</strong> us any
time, 24 hours a day -- we will respond during normal business hours.</font></p>

<h3><font face="Times New Roman"><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Hours of operation for
the<strong>:</strong> </font>

</h3>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman"><strong><a href="fileroom.htm">Environmental Quality Records File Room</a></strong><br>
    Tuesday, Wednesday and Thursday, 9:00 a.m. to 12:00 noon and 1:00 p.m. to 3:00 p.m.<br>
    Monday and Friday by appointment only - (<a href="phonefax.htm#fileroom">call
    for an appointment</a>).</font></p></li>
  <li><p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman"><strong>Hunting Permits and Safe Boating Certificates
    Office</strong> (including personal watercraft certificates)<br>
    Monday through Friday, 9:00 a.m. to 3:30 p.m.</font></p></li>
  <li><p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman"><strong><a href="../../store/index.htm">DEP
    Store</a>, where you can get maps and other useful
    publications</strong><br>
    Monday through Thursday, 9:00 a.m. to 3:30 p.m.</font></p></li>
  <li><p align="left"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>All other DEP Offices</b><br>
    Monday through Friday, 8:30 a.m. to 4: 30 p.m.</font></p></li>
</ul>

<p><font face="Times New Roman"><strong>Write </strong>us by directing your inquiry to the
appropriate bureau or office and sending your inquiry by U.S. mail to: <strong>The
Department of Environmental Protection, 79 Elm Street, Hartford, CT 06106-5127</strong>. </font></p>

<p><font face="Times New Roman"><a href="mailto:dep.webmaster@po.state.ct.us"><strong>E-mail</strong></a>
us any time. Because most of our information is not yet in electronic form, please be sure
to include your name, U.S. mail address, telephone&nbsp;and fax number. In many cases it
would be most efficient to respond to you by telephone or U.S. mail.</font></p>

<p><font face="Times New Roman"><strong>To give us feedback - </strong>Please take a
moment to fill out our users <a href="../../survey/survey.htm"><strong>survey</strong></a>.&nbsp;<br>
(For information requests, please use one of the methods above. No response will be given
to survey input.)</font></p>

<p align="center"><font face="Times New Roman"><a href="../aboutdep.htm">About
the DEP</a> | <a href="../thngwedo.htm">The Things We Do For You</a> | <a href="../mission.htm">Mission
Statements</a> | <a href="../progacti.htm">Programs and Activities</a>
</font></p>

